title: [Gyldemar Green, Forest]
description: Six oak trees extend to great heights and form a circle around a large cairn.  A black ring of ashes surrounds the cairn.  Moonlight filters down through the canopy of leaves, glinting off the stones.  A stillness blankets the area, no sound or movement noticeable.
